item.title: Bambi Board Game
item.dc:creator: virtuallysafe
item.description:
Bambi is an educational fun paced board game that teaches online safety in a fun and interactive way.
The board game takes 2-6 players, for ages 10 and up. Players navigate an engaging board filled with rewards and cyber risks, creating stronger passwords and avoiding dangerous internet attacks while trying to earn as much ruby as they can.
